        "title": "WebSocket Upgrade",
        "text": "",
        "diagram": "<svg viewBox=\"0 0 720 240\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <defs>\n              <marker id=\"ws-c2s\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"5\" markerHeight=\"5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"var(--dg-line)\"/></marker>\n              <marker id=\"ws-s2c\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"5\" markerHeight=\"5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"var(--dg-3)\"/></marker>\n              <marker id=\"ws-dup\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"5\" markerHeight=\"5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"var(--dg-1)\"/></marker>\n              <marker id=\"ws-ddown\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"5\" markerHeight=\"5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"var(--dg-3)\"/></marker>\n            </defs>\n            <!-- Client -->\n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"20\" width=\"120\" height=\"36\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"var(--dg-node)\" stroke=\"var(--dg-1)\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"100\" y=\"43\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-text)\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight:600>Client</text>\n            <!-- Server -->\n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"20\" width=\"120\" height=\"36\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"var(--dg-node)\" stroke=\"var(--dg-5)\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"600\" y=\"43\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-text)\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight:600>Server</text>\n            <!-- HTTP Upgrade Request -->\n            <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"65\" x2=\"538\" y2=\"65\" stroke=\"var(--dg-line)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ws-c2s)\"/>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"55\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-line)\" font-size=\"11\">GET /chat HTTP/1.1</text>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-line)\" font-size=\"11\">Upgrade: websocket</text>\n            <!-- 101 Switching Protocols -->\n            <line x1=\"538\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"105\" stroke=\"var(--dg-3)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ws-s2c)\"/>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-3)\" font-size=\"11\">Connection: Upgrade</text>\n            <!-- Bidirectional arrows -->\n            <path d=\"M160 140 L538 140\" stroke=\"var(--dg-1)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ws-dup)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M538 155 L160 155\" stroke=\"var(--dg-3)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ws-ddown)\"/>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"145\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-1)\" font-size=\"11\">Server pushes data</text>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"165\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-3)\" font-size=\"11\">Client sends data anytime</text>\n            <!-- Bottom bar -->\n            <rect x=\"130\" y=\"200\" width=\"460\" height=\"24\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"var(--cyan-dim)\"/>\n            <text x=\"360\" y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--dg-text)\" font-size=\"11\">WebSocket: persistent full-duplex connection after initial HTTP upgrade</text>\n          </svg>",
        "caption": "WebSocket upgrades an HTTP connection to a persistent full-duplex channel � both sides can send messages anytime without polling",
